#: ../../Y/yoyo-mode.rst:5
msgid "yoyo mode"
msgstr "yoyo mode"

#: ../../Y/yoyo-mode.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../Y/yoyo-mode.rst:9
msgid ""
"The state in which the system is said to be when it rapidly alternates "
"several times between being up and being down. Interestingly (and perhaps "
"not by coincidence), many hardware vendors give out free yoyos at Usenix "
"exhibits."
msgstr ""
"システムが、稼働中と停止中の間を何度も急速に交互に切り替わっていると言われるときの状態。興味深いことに(そしておそらく偶然ではなく)、多くのハードウェアベンダーがUsenixの展示会で無料のヨーヨーを配る。"

#: ../../Y/yoyo-mode.rst:12
msgid ""
"Sun Microsystems gave out logoized yoyos at SIGPLAN '88. Tourists staying at"
" one of Atlanta's most respectable hotels were subsequently treated to the "
"sight of 200 of the country's top computer scientists testing yo-yo "
"algorithms in the lobby."
msgstr ""
"Sun MicrosystemsはSIGPLAN "
"'88でロゴ入りのヨーヨーを配った。アトランタの最も格式ある一つのホテルに泊まっていた観光客は、その後、国内のトップ計算機科学者200人がロビーでヨーヨーのアルゴリズムを試す光景を目にすることになった。"
